snippet: Stan Wawrinka won the battle of the 30-year-olds by defeating Marcos Baghdatis of Cyprus 6-4, 7-6 (13) to win the Dubai Tennis Championships title Saturday....
lead_paragraph: Stan Wawrinka won the battle of the 30-year-olds by defeating Marcos Baghdatis of Cyprus 6-4, 7-6 (13) to win the Dubai Tennis Championships title Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Wawrinka Wins Dubai Title in Straight Sets Over Baghdatis
headline.main: Wawrinka Wins Dubai Title in Straight Sets Over Baghdatis
